	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi. I'm asking myself something.
<br />If you could magicaly add or change <em>one single</em> feature of the NES hardware, what will you do ?
<br />
<br />Myself, I'd be quite for replacing the 8x16 sprites per 16x8 sprites. That would be much more usefull to animate things, and even allow up to 16 "tiles" on the same scanline such of sprites.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


