<br />
<br /><strong>OR:</strong>
<br />CPU direct write access to PPU address space, with writes inserted "between" PPU reads.
<br />
<br /><strong>OR:</strong>
<br />Bring the video signal out to cart edge, as is done with the audio signal on the Famicom.

		

